 the simulations. This mild disagreement most\nlikely originates from inaccurate estimation of the instrumental beam at 30\nGHz.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Jul 2018 17:48:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 7 Jul 2018 09:08:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-09"}
