on (up\nto 20 hours) $\\gamma$-rays flares. We suggest that, in addition to DSA,\nstochastic acceleration by plasma turbulence may also play a role, especially\nin the shock downstream region and during the early stage when the shock\nAlfv\\'{e}n Mach number is small.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jul 2018 02:02:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Sep 2018 18:44:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
