at several\nlocal and global lifting theorems for analytic families of idempotents, along\nanalytic families of surjective Banach algebra homomorphisms, from our recent\npaper with B. Aupetit and M. Mbekhta, have analogues for elements of $E_p(A)$\nand $S_p(A)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jul 2018 13:04:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-05"}
